The '''groat''' was a bleating animal that inhabited several [[Planet/Legends|worlds]] and was usually domesticated for its [[Groat milk|milk]]. Groat [[Milk/Legends|milk]] was used in [[Toydarian/Legends|Toydarian]] cuisine, including [[Terratta]] and for making [[groat cheese]].

